name: Verify field is Auto Populated by default in WFH tab

testSteps.description: 1: Verify field is Auto Populated by default in WFH tab ({parentTab=Leave Management, childTab=Apply, defaultTab=Leave, tab=Work From Home, heading=Apply Leave / WFH / Comp Off / Out Duty / Change Request})

children.description: Given User is logged into MIS
When User is on MIS Home Page
When User clicks on "Apply" sub tab of "Leave Management" tab
And Verify "Apply Leave / WFH / Comp Off / Out Duty / Change Request" of "Apply" tab
When User clicks on "Work From Home" Tab
Then Verify "mobileNo" fields are auto populated
